{"id":10262,"date":"2024-01-09T18:19:34","date_gmt":"2020-06-09T12:49:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=10262"},"modified":"2024-02-04T21:19:16","modified_gmt":"2024-02-04T15:49:16","slug":"modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"These Modern False Ceiling Designs For Your Bedroom Will Make Heads Turn!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Turn the tables on the boring ceiling of your bedroom with these ideas!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your bedroom is like your den. At the end of the day, after crazy days at work or home, your bedroom rejuvenates you to face the next day with relative ease. That\u2019s why it is important that your bedroom feels like heaven to you and you wake you up to beauty and positivity every day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want your bedroom to look like an amazing space of art these modern <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom\/\">bedroom ceiling designs<\/a> will come to your rescue.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Usually, the ceilings or the fifth wall is left plain and unlooked. However, it can be a great piece of decor if you pay attention to it. An epitome of luxury, grandeur, and class these ceiling designs make any ordinary bedroom seem like a slice of heaven.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed with umpteen materials across textures and colours, do check out these modern false ceiling designs to revamp your bedroom like never before.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Vividly Vintage False Ceiling Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wooden bars tilted at an angle can make any ceiling look nostalgic and dreamy. Ideal for your master bedroom, this ceiling design does not require much of a shift and change. Just ideate it before you are planning a complete overhaul and this vintage design will make your bedroom stand out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181050\/vintage-modern-bedroom-ceiling.jpg\" alt=\"Vintage modern bedroom ceiling with wooden bars tilted at an angle can make any ceiling look nostalgic and dreamy.\" class=\"wp-image-10274\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181050\/vintage-modern-bedroom-ceiling.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181050\/vintage-modern-bedroom-ceiling-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181050\/vintage-modern-bedroom-ceiling-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181050\/vintage-modern-bedroom-ceiling-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A bedroom ceiling lined with chiseled wooden bars is matchless<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep Your False Ceiling Design Mesmerising Minimalistic<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A freshly painted white ceiling with wooden streaks are a magical combination for your bedroom. Go for this false ceiling design if you like all things minimalistic. It goes well with a modern bedroom design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180223\/minimalism-modern-bedroom-ceiling-pop-design.jpg\" alt=\"White ceiling with wooden streaks are a magical combination minimalistic modern bedroom ceiling designs\" class=\"wp-image-10266\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180223\/minimalism-modern-bedroom-ceiling-pop-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180223\/minimalism-modern-bedroom-ceiling-pop-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180223\/minimalism-modern-bedroom-ceiling-pop-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180223\/minimalism-modern-bedroom-ceiling-pop-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Minimalistic false ceiling designs set the tone for a pacifying bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Eyeing high end bedroom design ideas?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20123616\/Eyeing-high-end-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Amazing Opulence<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Not too ornamental and not too over the top, a slightly opulent false ceiling design never did any homeowner harm. Choose glass panels or crystals to make your false ceiling more inviting. The sheen of either of these materials will elevate the look and feel of your bedroom manifold.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180813\/opulence-modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-2020.jpg\" alt=\"Opulence modern bedroom false ceiling, choose glass panels or crystals to make your modern false ceiling more inviting.\" class=\"wp-image-10271\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180813\/opulence-modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-2020.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180813\/opulence-modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-2020-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180813\/opulence-modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-2020-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180813\/opulence-modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-2020-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Use glass, crystals and fiber panels to create an opulent false ceiling design for your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"941\" height=\"2348\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits.jpg\" alt=\"5 amazing benefits of having false ceiling in bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-50684\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits.jpg 941w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits-120x300.jpg 120w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits-410x1024.jpg 410w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits-768x1916.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits-616x1536.jpg 616w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits-821x2048.jpg 821w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/12145949\/bedroom-false-ceiling-benefits-150x374.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 941px) 100vw, 941px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gorgeous Grey<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The charm of subtle greys is simply unbeatable. You can play it up by lining it as a shed\/roof over your bedroom ceiling. Its uniformity and streamlined look grants a sense of completeness to your chamber.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180635\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-with-grey.jpg\" alt=\"Gorgeous grey modern false ceiling designs for bedroom its uniformity and streamlined look are unbeatable.\" class=\"wp-image-10269\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180635\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-with-grey.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180635\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-with-grey-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180635\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-with-grey-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180635\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-design-with-grey-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Opt for a full-grey false ceiling design to make your bedroom look more modern<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pleasantly Panelled<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Panels have the power of making your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interiors<\/a> look dynamic and chic. This false ceiling design also beautifully demarcates the space and lends a nice character to your bedroom. Choose this design if you want to stay up to date with home interior trends.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180901\/panelled-modern-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom ceiling design 2020, Panels have the power of making your bedroom interiors look dynamic and chic.\" class=\"wp-image-10272\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180901\/panelled-modern-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180901\/panelled-modern-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180901\/panelled-modern-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180901\/panelled-modern-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Fiber panels are an interesting choice for your bedroom\u2019s false ceiling design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxuriously Layered<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A multi-tiered false ceiling design looks breathtaking especially in a modern bedroom. This design makes a great use of umpteen materials like wood, fiber to exude class. Pick this false ceiling design to create an interesting bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180724\/modern-pop-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-interior.jpg\" alt=\"A multi-tiered modern bedroom ceiling design looks breathtaking and use of umpteen materials like wood, fibre to exude class\" class=\"wp-image-10270\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180724\/modern-pop-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-interior.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180724\/modern-pop-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-interior-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180724\/modern-pop-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-interior-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180724\/modern-pop-false-ceiling-designs-for-bedroom-interior-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A layered false ceiling design makes your bedroom impeccable<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Effusively Elegant<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Circular false ceiling designs look beautiful and can make your bedroom look delicate. Line it up in various layers and place lights around it to complete its amazing look. You can opt for this design with almost any bedroom interior plan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180134\/circular-elegant-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling.jpg\" alt=\"Circular modern bedroom ceiling designs look beautiful and can make your bedroom look delicate and effusively elegant\" class=\"wp-image-10265\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180134\/circular-elegant-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180134\/circular-elegant-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180134\/circular-elegant-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180134\/circular-elegant-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Circular false ceiling designs lend completeness and class to your chambers<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Soothingly Simple<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As they always say true beauty lies in simplicity. The same applies to false ceiling designs as well. Demarcated by lights, shapes, and edges, this seemingly simple false ceiling design looks amazing every time you look at it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180956\/simple-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling.jpg\" alt=\"Simple modern bedroom false ceiling demarcated by lights, shapes, and edges design looks fantastic\" class=\"wp-image-10273\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180956\/simple-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180956\/simple-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180956\/simple-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180956\/simple-modern-bedroom-false-ceiling-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A simple false ceiling design is perfect for a quintessentially modern bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stunning Star<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for an awe-inspiring false ceiling design for your teens or kids? Then this star-shaped false ceiling design will be an interesting choice for their bedroom. Pair it with subtle mood lighting to trigger their imagination and to make it a soothing decor highlight in their bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180459\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-with-stars.jpg\" alt=\"Star-shape modern bedroom ceiling pop design paired with subtle mood lighting and makes it soothing decor highlight\" class=\"wp-image-10268\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180459\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-with-stars.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180459\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-with-stars-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180459\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-with-stars-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09180459\/modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-with-stars-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">False ceiling designs in umpteen shapes work great for your child\u2019s bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wonderfully Wooden<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Almost like a block of art, a chunk of wood placed through a seemingly white ceiling works like absolute magic. This false ceiling design breaks the monotony of your bedroom and lets it have some sense of character and depth. If you want a modern, no-frills attached bedroom then you must definitely opt for this design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181144\/wooden-modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom ceiling a block of art, a chunk of wood placed through a seemingly white roof works like absolute magic.\" class=\"wp-image-10275\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181144\/wooden-modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181144\/wooden-modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181144\/wooden-modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/09181144\/wooden-modern-bedroom-ceiling-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Piece up a seamless chunk of wood as a false ceiling and make a chic chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>False ceiling designs are very popular for the fact that they make your bedroom look classy, artsy and worth spending time at! Choose your favourite designs from our recommendations and overhaul your chamber this season. Feel free to reach us for any further help you many need for the same.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Modern Bedroom False Ceiling Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Are there specific materials that are commonly used in modern bedroom ceiling designs?<\/strong><br>Common materials for modern bedroom ceilings include gypsum board, wood, metal, and decorative panels. The material is chosen based on your desired aesthetic and functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. What lighting options are popular for modern bedroom ceiling designs?<\/strong><br>Recessed lighting, pendant lights, and LED strips are popular options for modern bedroom ceiling designs. These lighting choices provide flexibility, style, and energy efficiency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Are there any considerations for incorporating technology or smart features into the ceiling design?<\/strong><br>Modern bedroom ceiling designs can integrate technology and smart features, such as motorised blinds, built-in speakers, or concealed wiring for home automation systems, enhancing convenience and functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. What role does sustainability and eco-friendly materials play in modern ceiling design?<\/strong><br>Sustainability is increasingly important in modern ceiling designs. Eco-friendly materials, like reclaimed wood or recycled metal, can be used to create environmentally responsible designs that reduce the carbon footprint of your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. What are some space-saving ideas for modern bedroom ceiling designs in smaller rooms?<\/strong><br>To maximise space in smaller bedrooms, opt for options like built-in storage, space-saving lighting fixtures, and light colour schemes that create an illusion of space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/different-type